page.title: 06SELBY HOUSING
page.content: THE HOUSING IN THE TOWN CENTRE IS EITHER OF THE SMALL TERRACED TYPE OR IS MORE MODERN. MANY OF THE SMALLER TERRACED HOUSES HAVE NO BACK GARDEN AND LEAD STRAIGHT OUT ONTO THE ROAD.MANY OF THEM ARE BEAUTIFULLY KEPT AND HAVE BEEN MODERNISED COMPLETELY. SOME NEW HOUSES BY TAY,COWEN AND PERSIMMON HAVE BEEN OR ARE BEING BUILT NEAR THE TOWN CENTRE.SOME OF THESES HOUSE ARE DETATCHED OTHERS ARE FLATS. NO HOUSES OR BUILDINGS IN SELBY ARE MORE THAN THREE STORIES HIGH,THE HIGHEST BUILDINGS BEING THE FLOUR MILL AND THE ABBEY.
